## DESIGN SYSTEM (IMMUTABLE — NEVER OVERRIDE)

```css
--pink:    #e0607e   /* primary CTA, alerts, highlights */
--gold:    #f7c948   /* secondary CTA, whale tier */
--green:   #64dc64   /* success, gains */
--red:     #ff4d4d   /* danger, loss */
--bg:      #050509   /* main background */
--text:    #f5f5f7   /* primary text */
--dim:     #888       /* muted text */
```

**CSS class system** (use these, don't invent new ones):
- Layout: `sec-pad`, `sec-eyebrow`, `sec-title`, `sec-bar`, `sec-header`, `sec-sub`
- Grids: `grid2`, `grid3`, `grid4`, `stat-card`, `slbl`, `sval`
- Cards: `card`, `card-sm`
- Buttons: `btn btn-primary`, `btn btn-pink`, `btn btn-gold`, `btn btn-green`, `btn btn-ghost`, `btn btn-outline`, `btn btn-sm`
- Badges: `badge b-pink`, `b-green`, `b-gold`, `b-blue`, `b-red`, `b-dim`
- Forms: `inp`, `field-inp`, `field-lbl`, `field-sel`
- Utility: `prog-bar`, `prog-fill`, `warn-bar`, `mode-pill`, `chat-msgs`
- Token gate overlay: `locked-overlay`, `locked-icon`, `locked-title`, `locked-sub`

