## ARCHITECTURE

```
app/
  layout.tsx          — Root layout, SEO metadata, SolanaProvider wrapper
  page.tsx            — Main SPA shell, wallet connect, all 35 section renders
  globals.css         — Entire design system (no Tailwind)
  api/
    price/route.ts    — Live $YST price from DexScreener
    holders/route.ts  — Live holder count (Birdeye → RPC fallback)
    ai.js             — Anthropic API proxy (rate-limited, wallet-gated)

components/
  Sidebar.tsx         — Nav sidebar (reads NAV from lib/constants.ts)
  TickerBar.tsx       — Top bar, live price, wallet button
  SolanaProvider.tsx  — Wallet adapter (Phantom + Solflare)
  sections/           — 35 individual section components

lib/
  constants.ts        — NAV structure, GATED_SECTIONS, token config, DEV_WALLETS
  holders.ts          — Static holder snapshot for instant gate bypass

public/
  og-image.png        — OG image for social sharing (1200×630)
  og-image.svg        — Source SVG
  manifest.json       — PWA manifest
  robots.txt          — SEO robots
  sitemap.xml         — SEO sitemap
```

