---

## WHEN ADDING A NEW SECTION

1. Create `components/sections/NewSection.tsx` with `'use client'` + Props interface
2. Add import to `app/page.tsx`
3. Add `'newsection'` to `SectionId` union type in `page.tsx`
4. Add render slot in the page section list
5. Add to `GATED_SECTIONS` in `lib/constants.ts` if gated
6. Add nav item in `lib/constants.ts` NAV structure
7. Run TypeScript check before pushing: `npx tsc --noEmit`

---

## BEFORE PUSHING — ALWAYS RUN

```bash
npx tsc --noEmit        # TypeScript errors = Vercel build failure
npx next build          # Full build test (optional but thorough)
```

